      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next adventure with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure a smooth, reliable ride. While it shows some light, expected wear from its time on the road, it remains a stylish and dependable choice that\u2019s ready for many more miles. Don't miss out on this well-cared-for gem!",
