    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project restorer or as a source for parts. The engine currently does not start, and there are visible signs of significant wear throughout, including noticeable body rust and a heavily worn interior with several tears in the upholstery. The transmission also requires a complete overhaul. While the car is mostly complete, it will require a trailer for transport and a significant investment of time and resources to return to a functional state.",
